file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: test1
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  "/foo":
    get:
      responses:
        202:
          description: "success"
    post:
      responses:
        202:
          description: "success"
      servers:
        - description: operation level server
          url: http://example.org/oplevel/test1
    servers:
     - description: path level server
       url: http://example.org/pathlevel/test1
  "/bar":
    get:
      responses:
        202:
          description: "success"
servers:
 - description: top level server
   url: http://example.org/toplevel/test1
